---
import ToolLayout from '../../layouts/ToolLayout.astro';

const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What is the maximum length of a Discord bio?",
    answer: "The strict character limit for a Discord bio (the 'About Me' section) is 190 characters. If your bio is longer, it will get cropped and you will not be able to save it."
  },
  {
    question: "Can I use formatting like bold or links in my Discord bio?",
    answer: "Yes, Discord bios support basic Markdown formatting. You can use asterisks for bold (**bold**) or italics (*italics*), underscores for underline (__underline__), and custom hyperlinks using standard markdown syntax."
  },
  {
    question: "Are emojis counted towards the character limit?",
    answer: "Yes, emojis count towards the 190-character limit. Custom emojis from servers can count as more characters because their underlying format includes the emoji name and ID (e.g. <:emojiname:123456789012345678>)."
  },
  {
    question: "Can I add server invite links to my bio?",
    answer: "Yes, you can paste server invite links or external social links into your Discord bio. However, keep in mind that URLs consume your 190-character budget quickly."
  },
  {
    question: "Is this bio generator free to use?",
    answer: "Yes, our Discord Bio Generator is 100% free to use. You can generate as many bio variations as you like without any limits or registration requirements."
  }
];
---

<ToolLayout
  title="Discord Bio Generator - Free Custom Profile Ideas"
  description="Generate cool, unique, and custom Discord bios for your profile. Optimize bios for gaming, aesthetic, cyberpunk, and witty themes."
  toolName="Discord Bio Generator"
  toolDescription="Create unique Discord bios under the strict 190-character limit. Customize by tone, toggle emojis or sparkles, and preview on a profile card."
  category="Writing Tools"
  faqs={faqs}
>
  <div slot="calculator" class="calc-card glass">
    <!-- Main Advanced Grid Layout -->
    <div class="calc-grid">
      <!-- Left Column: Generator Inputs -->
      <div class="calc-form-column">
        <div class="calc-form">
          <!-- Keywords Input -->
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="desc-input" class="icon-label">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="field-icon">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.862 4.487 1.687-1.688a1.875 1.875 0 1 1 2.652 2.652L10.582 16.07a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-1.897 1.13L6 18l.8-2.685a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 1.13-1.897l8.932-8.931Zm0 0L19.5 7.125M18 14v4.75A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 15.75 21H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 3 18.75V8.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 5.25 6H10" />
              </svg>
              Keywords or Hobbies
            </label>
            <input type="text" id="desc-input" class="form-input" placeholder="e.g. loves valorant, web developer, cat dad" value="gaming, coffee, web developer" />
          </div>

          <!-- Niche Tone -->
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="tone-select" class="icon-label">Bio Tone</label>
            <select id="tone-select" class="form-input" style="height: 48px; background: var(--color-bg); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 0 12px; color: var(--color-text);">
              <option value="gaming">Gaming / Competitive</option>
              <option value="cozy">Aesthetic / Cozy</option>
              <option value="cyber">Cyberpunk / Tech</option>
              <option value="witty">Funny / Witty</option>
              <option value="professional">Professional / Business</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <!-- Checkbox Toggles -->
          <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; background: var(--color-bg-alt); padding: 0.75rem 1rem; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
            <span style="font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-text-muted); text-transform: uppercase;">Decorative Elements</span>
            
            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.88rem;">
              <label style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; cursor: pointer; color: var(--color-text);">
                <input type="checkbox" id="emoji-check" checked style="accent-color: var(--color-brand); width: 16px; height: 16px;" />
                Include Emojis
              </label>
              <label style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; cursor: pointer; color: var(--color-text);">
                <input type="checkbox" id="sparkle-check" style="accent-color: var(--color-brand); width: 16px; height: 16px;" />
                Include Sparkles/Decorations
              </label>
              <label style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; cursor: pointer; color: var(--color-text);">
                <input type="checkbox" id="link-check" style="accent-color: var(--color-brand); width: 16px; height: 16px;" />
                Include Social Link Template
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Actions -->
          <div class="form-actions">
            <button type="button" id="generate-btn" class="calc-btn">Generate Bios</button>
            <button type="button" id="reset-btn" class="calc-btn-secondary">Reset Inputs</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Live Mockup Card -->
      <div class="calc-editor-column">
        <!-- Live Discord Profile Mockup Card -->
        <div class="discord-profile-card glass" style="background: #18191c; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; max-width: 320px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; border: 1px solid #202225; text-align: left; box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);">
          <!-- Top Banner -->
          <div style="background: #5865f2; height: 60px; width: 100%;"></div>

          <!-- Avatar & Badge Area -->
          <div style="position: relative; padding: 0 1rem; margin-top: -30px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end;">
            <!-- Avatar Container with Status Circle -->
            <div style="position: relative; display: inline-block;">
              <div style="width: 66px; height: 66px; border-radius: 50%; background: #2f3136; border: 6px solid #18191c; overflow: hidden; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #ffffff;">CF</div>
              <div style="position: absolute; bottom: 2px; right: 2px; width: 15px; height: 15px; border-radius: 50%; background: #43b581; border: 3px solid #18191c;"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Badge Box -->
            <div style="background: #2f3136; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px; display: flex; gap: 4px; align-items: center; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; color: #b9bbbe; margin-bottom: 4px;">
              <span>Online</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Profile Body -->
          <div style="padding: 1rem;">
            <!-- Name Header -->
            <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid #202225; padding-bottom: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
              <div style="font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 800; color: #ffffff;">Creators Feel</div>
              <div style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #b9bbbe; margin-top: 2px;">@creators_feel</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Custom Info Block -->
            <div style="font-size: 0.78rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; color: #b9bbbe;">
              <div>
                <strong style="color: #ffffff; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.68rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;">About Me</strong>
                <span id="discord-bio-text" style="color: #ffffff; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word;">Click a generated bio below to preview it here! 🎮☕💻</span>
              </div>

              <div>
                <strong style="color: #ffffff; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.68rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;">Discord Member Since</strong>
                <span>July 15, 2026</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Generated Results Section -->
    <div id="results-wrapper" class="hidden" style="margin-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px dashed var(--color-border); padding-top: 1.5rem;">
      <h3 style="font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0 0 1rem 0; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" style="width: 20px; height: 20px; color: var(--color-brand);">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 12 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 0 1-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 3 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1 1.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 0 1 3.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0 1 12 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 0 1 3.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 0 1 1.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 21 12Z" />
        </svg>
        Suggested Discord Bios
      </h3>

      <div class="bios-grid" id="generated-bios-container">
        <!-- Results dynamic content goes here -->
      </div>

      <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
        <button type="button" id="generate-more-btn" class="calc-btn" style="max-width: 200px; padding: 0 1.5rem;">Generate More</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div slot="about" class="editorial-content">
    <h2>Discord Bio Generator: Write Creative Profile About Me Text</h2>
    <div style="margin: 1.5rem 0; background: var(--color-bg-alt); padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: var(--radius-md); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-left: 4px solid var(--color-brand);">
      <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem;">
        🎮 <strong>Looking for a search-compliant username to pair with your new bio?</strong> Try our free <a href="/tools/discord-username-generator" style="color: var(--color-brand); text-decoration: underline;">Discord Username Generator</a> to secure a unique handle using aesthetic gaming niches.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h3>Introduction</h3>
    <p>
      In the digital era of communication, your Discord profile is your personal billboard. Whether you are chatting in server channels, networking with developers, or looking for teammate groupings, your "About Me" bio section defines how others perceive you. However, compiling a bio that captures your interest, lists your social accounts, and uses cool formatting options while fitting inside a tight character limit is difficult. Our free, interactive <strong>discord bio generator</strong> is designed to build creative, formatted bios automatically.
    </p>

    <h3>How to Use This Tool</h3>
    <p>
      To write and audit custom Discord bios in real-time, follow these simple directions:
    </p>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Keywords & Hobbies:</strong> Enter a few keywords, details, or hobbies that describe you.</li>
      <li><strong>Tone Selection:</strong> Choose a tone style that fits your persona (Gaming, Cozy/Aesthetic, Cyberpunk/Tech, Witty, or Professional).</li>
      <li><strong>Toggles:</strong> Check options to insert custom emoji layouts, sparkle designs, or social link place-markers.</li>
      <li><strong>Generate List:</strong> Click **Generate Bios** to construct 5 custom bio variations.</li>
      <li><strong>Mockup & Copy:</strong> Click any generated bio block to see it previewed in the Discord card mockup, and click the copy chip button to save it.</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>What is Discord Bio</h3>
    <p>
      A <strong>discord bio</strong> (officially known as the "About Me" box) is a text space in your user profile card. It supports up to 190 characters of text, emojis, links, and markdown formatting. It lets you display details about who you are, what games you play, what servers you run, or where else people can find you online.
    </p>

    <h3>How Does It Work?</h3>
    <p>
      The generator merges your seed hobbies with pre-formatted structure scripts:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Keyword Parsing:</strong> Cleans up your hobbies list and integrates them into natural, conversational phrases.</li>
      <li><strong>Decoration Integration:</strong> Adds aesthetic borders, line separators, or emojis based on your selections.</li>
      <li><strong>Character Cap Auditing:</strong> Cuts off sentences cleanly before they hit 190 characters to avoid browser saving crashes.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Example Calculation</h3>
    <p>
      Let's look at how a custom bio character budget is calculated:
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Input Description:</strong> `"loves gaming, developer"`<br />
      <strong>Tone:</strong> `"Gaming / Competitive"`<br />
      <strong>Toggles:</strong> `"Include Emojis"`, `"Include Sparkles"`, `"Include Social Link Template"`
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Bio Construction Process:</strong><br />
      ✦ Base copy: `"*Loves gaming & developing*"` $\rightarrow$ <strong>26 characters</strong> (with markdown italics).<br />
      ✦ Sparkle decorations: `"✧ ✦ ✧"` $\rightarrow$ <strong>5 characters</strong>.<br />
      ✦ Emojis: `"🎮💻"` $\rightarrow$ <strong>4 characters</strong> (standard emojis count as 2 UTF-16 bytes).<br />
      ✦ Social link: `"| links: cf.gg"` $\rightarrow$ <strong>15 characters</strong>.<br />
      ✦ Combined output: `"✧ Loves gaming & developing ✧ 🎮💻 | links: cf.gg"` $\rightarrow$ <strong>50 characters</strong>.<br />
      ✦ Compliance audit: `50 < 190 characters`.
    </p>
    <p>
      This bio fits within Discord's 190-character limit with a remaining budget of 140 characters.
    </p>

    <h3>Features</h3>
    <p>
      This <strong>free discord bio generator</strong> offers several tools:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Interactive Profile Preview Mockup:</strong> Review how your bio wraps, displays, and fits inside a dark-themed Discord card.</li>
      <li><strong>Real-Time Character Count Safety:</strong> Every generated option is pre-audited to ensure it never exceeds the 190-character ceiling.</li>
      <li><strong>Markdown Ready Formatting:</strong> Generates italic hooks and clean column dividers automatically.</li>
      <li><strong>Pill-Shaped Tactile Copy Buttons:</strong> Instantly copy your favorite bio with a single click.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Who Should Use This Tool?</h3>
    <p>
      This generator is designed for:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Esports Competitors:</strong> Listing roles (e.g. `Duelist main`), team names, and social links.</li>
      <li><strong>Aesthetic Community Profiles:</strong> Writing soft, cozy bios with aesthetic emojis.</li>
      <li><strong>Software Developers:</strong> Showing programming stacks (e.g. `Astro / TS`) and linking to GitHub repositories.</li>
      <li><strong>Writers & Creatives:</strong> Creating witty, humorous bios to showcase personality.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</ToolLayout>

